title: The Natural Nurse
content:
FLU SHOT OR NOT? <!--more--> Join Host Ellen Kamhi, PhD, RN, AHG, AHN-BC to find out information about the safety, efficacy, ingredients and politics of the ‘FLU SHOT”.
Have you had one?
Why or why not, what has been your experience.
Dr Kamhi will also share a specific NATURAL FLU Protection Protocol that you can use to improve your natural defenses.
